---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kigali - Rwanda's Vibrant Capital City">
  <Header />
  
  <div style="padding-top: 120px;" class="s">
    <div class="s-narrow" style="margin: 0 auto;">
      <span class="s-label">Capital City</span>
      <h1 class="s-heading">Kigali<br><em>Where Africa Shines</em></h1>
      <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <img src="/images/kigali_city_view_1763982611088.png" alt="Kigali cityscape" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;">
      </div>
      <div class="s-body" style="max-width: 100%;">
        <p>Kigali is Africa's cleanest and most modern capital — a city of surprising beauty, extraordinary hospitality, and deep meaning. From the moving Kigali Genocide Memorial to the vibrant Inema Arts Centre and an exploding culinary scene, Kigali demands time beyond a simple transit stop.</p>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gold);">Why Visit Kigali</h3>
        <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; list-style-position: inside;">
          <li>🏛️ Kigali Genocide Memorial — one of Africa's most essential museums</li>
          <li>🎨 Inema Arts Centre & Niyo Arts Gallery — contemporary Rwandan creativity</li>
          <li>🍽️ World-class dining at Meza Malonga, The Hut, and Filini</li>
          <li>🛍️ Kimironko Market — authentic local shopping experience</li>
          <li>🌃 Nightlife in Kiyovu and Kimihurura neighborhoods</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="info-box" style="background: var(--bg2); padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);">
          <h4 style="color: var(--gold);">Visa Information</h4>
          <p>Kigali International Airport (KGL) offers e-visa arrivals for most nationalities. Apply online at 
          <a href="/visa" style="color: var(--gold);">irembo.gov.rw</a> or let us handle the process for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>